<p>I am implementing Cascading dropdownlist in my MVC Application. I am using Json result to get the output. My problem is while selecting the Business category from one dropdown the service type to the corresponding business didn't get loaded in the second dropdown.</p>  <p>My code in View is </p>  <pre><code> &lt;div&gt;            @Html.DropDownList("Business", "Select the Business Category")        &lt;/div&gt;        &lt;div&gt;            &lt;label&gt;Select the Service Type&lt;/label&gt;            &lt;select id="Buname" name="buname"&gt;&lt;/select&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;       $(function () {            $('#Business').change(function () {               debugger;               $.getJSON('/Appt/Categories/' + $('#Business').val(), function (data) {                    var items = '&lt;option&gt; Select&lt;/option&gt;'                   $.each(data, function (i, buname) {                        items += "&lt;option value='" + buname.Value + "'&gt;" + buname.Text +                           "&lt;/option&gt;";                   });                    $("#Buname").html(items);                });             });        });       &lt;/script&gt; </code></pre>  <p>My controller Code is </p>  <pre><code> public JsonResult Categories(int id)         {             SYTEntities db = new SYTEntities();             var business = from s in db.tblBusinessCategories                            where s.CategoryId == id                            select s;             return Json(new SelectList(business.ToArray(),"BusinessID", "BusinessName"), JsonRequestBehavior.AllowGet);         } </code></pre>  <p>Am getting an error in return Json Line as shown in the below diagram <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/8fBuy.png" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/8fBuy.png" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>  <p>Can anyone please help me?</p>  <p>Thanks in Advance.</p>